<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.1">
<l>cilaiyilaṅku poṉṉāḻi tiṇpaṭaitaṇ ṭoṇcaṅka meṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>malaiyilaṅku tōḷnāṉkē maṟṟavaṉuk keṟṟēkā ṇeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>mulaiyilaṅku pūmpayalai muṉpōṭa vaṉpōṭi yirukkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kalaiyilaṅku moḻiyāḷar kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“A bow, shining gold discus, strong battle club, and bright conch,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>“Also, what kind of four mountain[-like] shining shoulders has he? Look!”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>Before the blossoming [love-sick] pallor that shines on her breasts spreads,</l>
<l rend="indent">she is running to love.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram with those</l>
<l rend="indent">in whose speech learning shines?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
